    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊刚才突然又想起来，昨晚的梦里我好像还拿着每日一道的书，然后你问我是不是可做完了，我说确实诶，你怎么知道，好神奇！</p><p><img  src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/25/6D9dVy5r1bHYtwa.png"  ><span class="image-caption">呜呜呜想要抱抱</span></p><hr><blockquote><p>每日歌词<br>欢迎投稿</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><img  src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/25/pUkE3Pj6dKAXSMG.jpg"  ><span class="image-caption">让你不用观察嘻嘻嘻</span><br>正好最近看的乔布斯传里还看到了它</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>历史上的今天<br>小童携保镖参加了运动会！</p></blockquote><hr><p>李尔又来骗人啦！</p><p><img  src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/25/VUT3SKNbFHW7QD5.jpg"  ><span class="image-caption">每天一道！</span></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
